cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything.
This festive little Ford has cold A/C, p/s, p/w, p/dl, 5-spd, cassette. 143k miles. Fresh fluids, tires, wipers, door seals. Perfect 1st car.
The Trooper is an aircraft hanger on wheels; it will carry ALL the things. Slow but sturdy. 4WD, auto, cloth, A/C, power everything. Moving or homeless? This one's for you!
